\v 55 They \w were|strong="H1121"\w* given Hebron \w in|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H1121"\w* \w land|strong="H4940"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Judah \w and|strong="H1121"\w* its surrounding \w pasturelands|strong="H4054"\w*.
