\m 
\v 59 Ashan, Juttah, \w and|strong="H4054"\w* Beth-shemesh, together \w with|strong="H4294"\w* their \w pasturelands|strong="H4054"\w*.
\m 
\v 60 \w And|strong="H4054"\w* from the tribe \w of|strong="H4054"\w* Benjamin they were given Gibeon, Geba, Alemeth, \w and|strong="H4054"\w* Anathoth, together with their \w pasturelands|strong="H4054"\w*. So they had thirteen cities \w in|strong="H4054"\w* all among their families.
